    "It helps multimodal LLM agents learn from past mistakes and successful trades.",
    "By reflecting on these experiences, agents can avoid repeating errors and improve 3 The retrieval types include short-term, medium/long-term market impacts, asset price increase/decrease, market trends bearish/bullish, news/reports, etc."
